{"tid":780732,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【股王失威】騰訊大股東Naspers即市曾跌近一成","createTime":"2018-08-15T11:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T12:23:45.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e823e562ef4128101586700fccbd7e5d4539f48d","tid":780732,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"騰訊（700）業績遜預期，連帶持有33.17%騰訊最大股東，南非傳媒集團Naspers急跌。Naspers於騰訊業績公佈前下跌1.1%，惟業績公佈之後跌幅擴大，曾跌9%，現時跌約6%。<br />\n<br />\nNaspers總部位於南非開普敦，創立於1915年，起初只是一間出版商，1994年在約翰內斯堡交易所上市，業務包括電子商務、電子支付、付費電視以及印刷媒體等，在非洲、印度、巴西都有很大影響力。根據Naspers最新年報顯示，持股超過5%的單一股東就只有南非政府的主權基金Public Investment Corporation of South Africa，持有13.97%股權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180815/58567520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180815%2F58567520&d=FMTmREmLMwwt0A%2F8c0IlfTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=418ec3aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180815%2F58567520&h=34439eff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180815/58567520</a>"},{"pid":"7be7e065117f6a50ca8b5c8c1410170aa2e48b4a","tid":780732,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:23:45.000Z","msg":"要死，大家一齊死。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">有1-2手</span>"}]}